data.description: This amazing three-bedroom home with the potential for a fourth bedroom and two baths has an open and modern feel with plenty of room for entertaining and a fully finished basement. This beauty is located in the Fall Creek subdivision. As you walk in, you are greeted with high ceilings and plenty of light cascading through the large front windows. vaulted ceilings, and a lot of natural light. updated gourmet kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, stainless steel appliances, including a double oven, and beautiful granite countertops. The kitchen is open and spacious, perfect for gatherings. The lower level can be used as a family room, office, or entertaining area. Possibly turn it into a bedroom and enjoy the oversized bathroom with a jacuzzi tub. This home was built to be virtually soundproof and properly insulated with commercial-grade fire-resistant mineral wool. This basement is where you can have fun and make memories. A beautiful mini bar and an open area where the pool table, hockey table, shuffleboard, and darts can be optional for your entertainment. This home is fully fenced and well cared for, with a new AC, sump pump, carpet, paint, the driveway has fresh blacktop, new roof, and siding.
